{"tid":1318150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候將警察呢支槍頭直指執政四人幫","createTime":"2019-07-15T01:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T06:57:59.000Z","uid":74778,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d6599ba684bce4fc3d9155695ffe70215c514815","tid":1318150,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jUdFPdc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjUdFPdc.png&h=913a1875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本佢地四個仆街，同埋果一堆二堆陷家剷建制議員<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XBG8dFE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXBG8dFE.png&h=230baba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以咁舒適咁坐係個立法會城堡入面刀槍不入，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">正正係因為有三萬警察大軍把關！</span></strong>只要佢地一消失，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暴 政 必 亡！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我當全香港30,000警力，有1/3係運動一開始既時候，69 612，已經係濫竽充數/唔支持條條例...總之就無心戀戰<br />\n<br />\n仲有果20,000我當真係好有戰力，但當中有一半有羞恥心，喺水刮隊長事件之後覺得自己陣形做d偷雞摸狗既事，又或者經過咁長時間既與民為敵，已經無曬軍心，又或者諗通左自己其實只係四人幫推出黎送死既馬前卒...總之就想撤退，已經攰<br />\n<br />\n咁即係全香港，<span style=\"color: blue;\">宜家反對政府粗暴施政既巿民，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">同果四人幫同班仆街議員既距離，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只係淨返呢10,000警力！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMWW65i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMWW65i.png&h=a6a35fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢10,000人，係已經經歷69 612 71，已經比蘆葦蔥 李+超 fake過無數咁多鑊，再加上光復上水沙田流血事件...<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">你覺得佢地仲有幾想工作？有幾想出黎比全民爆粗侮辱？有幾想比四人幫利用？</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我既意思係！如果你同我講根本四人幫都係傀儡，背後係中聯辦！<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">咁 四 幫 唔 聽 中 聯 辦 支 笛 又 如 何？</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本林鄭自己都想請辭，想走，大陸唔放過佢，香港人唔放過佢，佢等仆街。我想講既係根本香港警隊都係面對緊同一樣問題，我地根本唔洗想佢地死，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要可以收歸己用</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣工作應該全面進場！</span></span></strong>佢地流既血夠佢地動搖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQZd9nF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQZd9nF.gif&h=f49e2d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文宣工作針對偏黃警察，不出一個月警察潰不成軍！<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加強文攻，解決左30,000警力之後，將運動回歸5大訴求！直搗黃龍！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d68e665bd034bed3651ad898de34f7d1c3e249b1","tid":1318150,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925b5efd8cd3d9209d90dca9b395a80ca88f6c2b","tid":1318150,"uid":218575,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:38:22.000Z","msg":"一早要拋番個波俾政府班碌柒啦 推"},{"pid":"2f92b96fd504f9d2d17203bb69a18eb994789ea1","tid":1318150,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:41:19.000Z","msg":"歸根究底都係政府既錯"},{"pid":"2f9b7b09202a7641eba711021b47138532f0d644","tid":1318150,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c306bc5f2ae8ac079830eb080719872aa4f892b","tid":1318150,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:43:44.000Z","msg":"仲有