沙田流血事件...<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">你覺得佢地仲有幾想工作？有幾想出黎比全民爆粗侮辱？有幾想比四人幫利用？</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我既意思係！如果你同我講根本四人幫都係傀儡，背後係中聯辦！<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">咁 四 幫 唔 聽 中 聯 辦 支 笛 又 如 何？</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本林鄭自己都想請辭，想走，大陸唔放過佢，香港人唔放過佢，佢等仆街。我想講既係根本香港警隊都係面對緊同一樣問題，我地根本唔洗想佢地死，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要可以收歸己用</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣工作應該全面進場！</span></span></strong>佢地流既血夠佢地動搖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQZd9nF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQZd9nF.gif&h=f49e2d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文宣工作針對偏黃警察，不出一個月警察潰不成軍！<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加強文攻，解決左30,000警力之後，將運動回歸5大訴求！直搗黃龍！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:47:33.000Z","msg":"其實3餅狗狗唔係全部都係前線<br />\n你有無見過出超過1餅狗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比例啫"},{"pid":"5339fea87505bfec258ce5a8377445d61c1f072e","tid":1318150,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:23:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3c8187c69a0049396f273ad24152f4bb889c168","tid":1318150,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjq1GXV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkjq1GXV.png&h=afc4e8cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n遍 地 開 花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"67d65fd5eef61e912435d4c8bd67eebfbff626aa","tid":1318150,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3f002c4e3498fbde7c4eabee31157d55c1be89","tid":1318150,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}